fields.title: Introduction to Structured Bags
fields.description:
# Objective

Handbags are a staple job in the accessories industry. To dedicate to this profession it is necessary to know and handle the materials to make them and the manufacturing techniques. In this course you will learn and learn the fundamentals of materials and container assembly.

fields.title: Professional Tutu Making
fields.description:
# Objective

You will make a life-size professional tutu that will fit completely finished at the end of the workshop. This involves pattern making, cutting and making of all pieces.

fields.title: Hat Making
fields.description:
# Objective

With this course you can make felt hats manually. We will see the whole process step by step until we reach the end so that you can make and design hats without difficulties.
